name: Garbage Game (madisartdump)
description:
Play a stray kitty just trying to get its next meal without using up all its 9 lives. 

Use left and right arrow keys to move. Run into garbage cans on the ground to eat them, but don’t let them fall on you! Eat as much garbage as you can until you run out of lives. Good luck!

Credits: 

Sound Assets: Shapeforms Audio Free Sound Effects by Shapeforms, Animals! By Olan, and Platformer Music Pack LITE by VOiD1 Gaming

Everything else was created by me. :)

Enjoy!
